headline: Is There Still Room to Run for W. R. Berkley After a 36% Rally?
summary: Thinking about what to do with W. R. Berkley stock right now? You’re not alone. After all, this insurance giant has been the quiet achiever of the sector, with a stock price that keeps rewarding patient investors. Over the last year alone, W. R. Berkley’s shares have climbed an impressive 35.9%, and the momentum continues, with an increase of 0.9% in the last week and 6.3% over the past month.
